long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use this extension to find cheap cars for sale in USA. Select your favorite auto maker or the state you live to see some real cheap used cars listed for sale at prices starting for $500, $1000, $2000, $5000 or less.

Autopten is search engine especially made to help people with low budget find the most affordable used cars for sale in the US.

If you are looking for cars for sale priced for $500, $1000, $2000 or less than $5000, this Chrome extension may help you in your search.

This extension is very EASY to use. Just select your favorite brand and the state where you live, push the SEARCH button, and it will show the list of cars for sale found on our database, plus some other offered at auction from same brand. These vehicles are sorted by the lowest price.

You can also download our Android App from:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.autopten.cheapcarsforsale

Search by "Autopten" or "Cheap Cars" on the Google Play Store to find out Android App.

You can also join us at http://www.autopten.com/
